	Boutique Bellydancersize classes! \\nSpecialized classes. Superior core wo
	rkout. Strengthens & coordinates muscle groups in the trunk\\\, spine & ar
	ms. Improves posture & flexibility. Students will learn the basic steps\\\
	, undulations\\\, shimmies\\\, isolations\\\, tuxseem and more. \\nAll Age
	s. \\nGroup classes at Phinney Center. A focused gym that provides a sense
	 of connection. Zaphara’s classes go beyond physical fitness\\\, including
	 a broader sense of self care\\\, including sleep\\\, nutrition\\\, skin h
	ealth\\\, stress management & socializing. \\nStarts the 1st Thursday of t
	he Month \\n7:00 pm – 8:00 pm – Beginners \\n7:45 pm – 9:00 pm Intermediat
	e – Advanced \\n4 weeks: $80\\\, Drop-ins: $27 per class \\nTaught by Zaph
	ara\\\, Master Bellydance Instructor & Performer \\nSign up and pay online
	: bellydancingbyzaphara.com/classes\n\nhttps://www.phinneycenter.org/event
	/boutique-bellydancersize-classes/2026-04-02/\n\nFrom Phinney Neighborhood
	 Association (PNA)
